# 六、Registration Events

客户注册事件。

```
CustomerRegistered

CustomerActivated

CustomerImported

CustomerVerified
```

所有客户进入系统。

均产生事件。

---

# 七、Profile Events

资料变化。

```
CustomerProfileUpdated

CustomerPhoneChanged

CustomerEmailChanged

CustomerAddressChanged

CustomerBirthdayUpdated
```

Profile：

全部事件化。

---

# 八、Membership Events

会员变化。

```
MembershipCreated

MembershipActivated

MembershipUpgraded

MembershipRenewed

MembershipExpired
```

Membership Aggregate。

统一事件。

---

# 九、Relationship Events

关系变化。

```
RelationshipCreated

RelationshipRemoved

ReferralCreated

AdvisorAssigned

HouseholdCreated

HouseholdMemberAdded
```

形成：

Relationship Timeline。

---

# 十、Growth Events

成长事件。

```
GrowthStageChanged

CustomerScoreChanged

CustomerLevelChanged

CustomerAchievementUnlocked
```

成长：

全部记录。

---

# 十一、Value Events

客户价值变化。

```
CustomerValueChanged

LifetimeValueCalculated

RFMCalculated

CustomerSegmentChanged
```

AI。

重新计算。

同样发布事件。

---

# 十二、Lifecycle Events

生命周期变化。

```
CustomerBecameLead

CustomerActivated

CustomerDormant

CustomerReactivated

CustomerLost
```

生命周期。

完全事件驱动。

---

# 十三、Interaction Events

客户互动事件。

```
StoreVisited

ConsultationCreated

MessageReceived

AppointmentBooked

FeedbackSubmitted

ProductCollected
```

Customer Timeline。

来源：

Interaction Event。

---

# 十四、AI Events

AI 行为事件。

```
AIInsightGenerated

RecommendationGenerated

RiskDetected

PurchaseIntentDetected

ChurnRiskDetected
```

AI。

也是 Event Producer。

---

# 十五、System Events

系统事件。

```
CustomerMerged

CustomerArchived

CustomerRestored

CustomerDeleted(Logical)

DataSynchronized
```

保证：

系统一致性。

